## ğŸ” Permissions

Unveil uses the following permissions:

- `activeTab`: Modify the current tab
- `scripting`: Inject scripts/styles
- `tabs`: Track the active tab for execution
- `storage`: (future) Save per-site preferences

> ğŸ”’ Unveil runs 100% locally â€” no tracking, no data collection, no cloud calls.

